name: Banner of the Maid - Marie Therese / 圣女战旗 - 玛丽·特蕾兹
description:
依然是用一个全身图片训练的，更换姿势还是略有一定的难度，使劲加权重。

人物提示词看情况和权重配合使用能尽量改变动作，Marie Therese+0.2都行。

发饰原因，AI概率画成双马尾。

Google Translate:

It is still training with only one full-body picture, and it is still a little difficult to change the posture, so increase the weight.

Character prompts can be used in conjunction with weights to change actions depending on the situation, Marie Therese+0.2 is also possible.

modelVersions.name: Marie Therese v2.0
modelVersions.description:
我发现这角色脑袋下面都是对称的，就镜像了几张图尝试抵消那一成不变的动作。

Google Translate:

I found that the character below the head is symmetrical, so I mirrored a few pictures to try to offset the unchanging movements.
